Sentencas: Nanostructured perovskite oxides of Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) were synthesized through the co-precipitation method.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: The thermal decomposition, phase formation and thermal expansion behavior of BSCF were characterized by thermogravimetric analysis, X-ray diffraction (XRD), and dilatometry, respectively.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: XRD peaks were indexed to a cubic perovskite structure with a Pm3m (221) space group.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: All the combined oxides produced the desired perovskite-phase BSCF.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: The microstructures were characterized by scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and transmission electron microscopy (TEM).
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: The TEM analysis showed that BSCF powders had uniform nanoparticle sizes and high homogeneity.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: The cross-sectional SEM micrograph of BSCF exhibited a continuous and no delaminated layer from the electrolyte-supported cell.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) of BSCF was 16.2 x 10(-6) K-1 at a temperature range of 600 degrees C to 800 degrees C. Additional experiments showed that the TEC of BSCF is comparable to that of Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (SDC) within the same temperature range.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9

Sentencas: The results demonstrate that BSFC is a promising cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: THERMAL EXPANSION BEHAVIOR OF THE Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (BSCF) WITH Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9
